# Decision log

Architecture Decision Records (ADRs) for {{PROJECT_NAME}}. Each records one
durable decision: its context, what was decided, and why. Records are
append-only — superseded ones are marked, never deleted, so the reasoning trail
survives.

The currently-binding distilled rules live in [`.forge/directives.md`](../../.forge/directives.md)
and are injected into every session. Add decisions with `/forge:decide`.

